OL,3,CCommunity group founder warns
OL,4,Cneurodivergent adults are falling
OL,5,Cthrough the gaps
OL,7,FITV Granada Reports correspondent Andy
OL,8,FBonner asked how Reet Good Wood was
OL,9,Fmaking a difference.
OL,11,FThe founder of a community group is
OL,12,Fwarning that adults with autism and
OL,13,FADHD are falling between the gaps of
OL,14,Fsociety.
OL,16,FReet Good Wood, a community interest
OL,17,Fcompany in Leigh, Greater Manchester,
OL,18,Fempowers neurodivergent people from
OL,19,Facross the north west through its
OL,20,Fworkshops to upcycle reclaimed
OL,21,Ffurniture.
