OL,3,CCommunity group founder warns
OL,4,Cneurodivergent adults are falling
OL,5,Cthrough the gaps
OL,7,FThe not-for-profit group was created
OL,8,Flast summer by Ruth, a furniture
OL,9,Fartist with autism and undiagnosed
OL,10,FAttention Deficit Hyperactivity
OL,11,FDisorder (ADHD).
OL,13,FIt uses therapeutic furniture painting
OL,14,Fand other creative methods to help
OL,15,Fpeople develop confidence, express
OL,16,Fthemselves and reduce social isolation.
OL,18,FShe said, "Because people look a
OL,19,Fcertain way and present a certain way,
OL,20,Fpeople don't necessarily think that we
OL,21,Fstruggle.
