OL,7,F"We do often get overlooked and
OL,8,Fthere's just a massive gap in service
OL,9,Ffor people like us."
OL,11,FThe group helps reduce waste and
OL,12,Fbrings pre-loved items back to life
OL,13,Fwith custom designs.
OL,15,FBut it is about more than
OL,16,Fsustainability.
