OL,7,FIt links adults who can often feel
OL,8,Fisolated and misunderstood - whether
OL,9,Fthey have been diagnosed or not - and
OL,10,Fgives them vital support from their
OL,11,Fpeers.
OL,13,FAnthony and his wife have started
OL,14,Fattending the workshops together.
OL,16,FHe said, "I've always struggled in
OL,17,Fsocial situations.
