OL,7,F"So to have somewhere where I can come
OL,8,Fand be, and everyone else has got the
OL,9,Fsame sort of issues, it's a great
OL,10,Fplace."
OL,12,FJasmine, who has ADHD, added, "I've
OL,13,Fgot 3 kids so our life is chaos.
OL,15,F"So to come here and all I've got to
OL,16,Fthink about is painting this piece of
OL,17,Ffurniture, it's just nice."
