OL,3,CCommunity group founder warns
OL,4,Cneurodivergent adults are falling
OL,5,Cthrough the gaps
OL,7,FNeurodivergence is a non-medical term
OL,8,Fthat refers to any structured and
OL,9,Fconsistent way that brains work
OL,10,Fdifferently from the majority of
OL,11,Fpeople.
OL,13,FEveryone in the group has had a late
OL,14,Fneurodivergent diagnosis or is waiting
OL,15,Ffor a diagnosis.
OL,17,FThe ReMade Women group shares the
OL,18,Fcreative space in Spinner's Mill, a
OL,19,Fhub with affordable rooms for
OL,20,Findependent artists and creatives,
OL,21,Fwith Reet Good Wood.
