OL,3,CCommunity group founder warns
OL,4,Cneurodivergent adults are falling
OL,5,Cthrough the gaps
OL,7,FAlice, who runs the group, said,
OL,8,F"People who are diagnosed with some
OL,9,Fkind of neurodivergence are sent
OL,10,Fthrough to mental health services and
OL,11,Fexperience things like the CBT
OL,12,Freferrals, which aren't necessarily
OL,13,Fthe right thing because it's
OL,14,Feffectively telling people that
OL,15,Fthey're not thinking the right way
OL,16,Fwhen in fact there's nothing wrong
OL,17,Fwith us."
OL,19,FSuch is the level of demand that the
OL,20,Fworkshops are fully booked until May.
