OL,3,CCommunity group founder warns
OL,4,Cneurodivergent adults are falling
OL,5,Cthrough the gaps
OL,7,FThey sell some of the furniture to
OL,8,Fgenerate income but still need
OL,9,Ffinancial help to continue the venture.
OL,11,FA crowdfunder is currently open,
OL,12,Foffering supporters the chance to win
OL,13,Fa renovated item.
OL,15,FUltimately, Ruth wants to upscale the
OL,16,Fservice itself to help as many people
OL,17,Fas possible across the country.
OL,19,FBut that will happen only if she can
OL,20,Ffind stable long-term funding to
OL,21,Frealise her dream
